OL,3,CHospitals to be offered cash
OL,4,Cincentives for tackling 12-hour A&E
OL,5,Cwait times
OL,7,FCash incentives are to be offered to
OL,8,Fhospitals that do not leave patients
OL,9,Fwaiting in A&E for 12 hours or more,
OL,10,Funder new NHS England plans.
OL,12,FUp to #150 million will be put aside
OL,13,Ffor hospitals with the "highest
OL,14,Fperformance" and "greatest improvement
OL,15,Fin performance", according to the
OL,16,Fplans.
