OL,5,Cwait times
OL,7,FThe use of virtual wards will also
OL,8,Fincrease in order to free up space in
OL,9,Femergency departments, with hospitals
OL,10,Fencouraged to refer more patients
OL,11,Fthere.
OL,13,FThe NHS has "hailed" its own
OL,14,Fimprovements in a letter to hospital
OL,15,Ftrusts, claiming that last year was
OL,16,Fthe first outside of the pandemic
OL,17,Fsince 2009 that more patients in A&E
OL,18,Fwere seen within four hours.
