OL,3,CHospitals to be offered cash
OL,4,Cincentives for tackling 12-hour A&E
OL,5,Cwait times
OL,7,FThe latest figures showed more than
OL,8,F42,000 people waited more than 12
OL,9,Fhours in A&E departments in April,
OL,10,Fdown slightly from 42,968 in March.
OL,12,FHowever, around 74% of patients were
OL,13,Fseen within four hours last month. The
OL,14,FNHS target is 76%.
OL,16,FThis target will rise to 78% by March
OL,17,F2025, which still remains below the
OL,18,F95% target set out in 2010.
