OL,5,Cwait times
OL,7,FSarah-Jane Marsh, national director
OL,8,Ffor urgent and emergency care at NHS
OL,9,FEngland, hailed the "hard work of NHS
OL,10,Fstaff" for what she described as a
OL,11,Fyear of "considerable progress in the
OL,12,Frecovery of urgent and emergency care
OL,13,Fservices", but added: "There is still
OL,14,Fmuch further to go."
OL,16,FMr Anandaciva said the plan for
OL,17,F"gradual improvements" comes at a time
OL,18,Fwhen the health service is "in crisis".
