OL,7,F"It has been nearly a decade since A&E
OL,8,Fperformance targets were reliably met,
OL,9,Fand there is little prospect of
OL,10,Fperformance substantially improving in
OL,11,Fthe near future.
OL,13,F"It is patients and staff who are
OL,14,Fbearing the brunt of the sharp
OL,15,Fdeterioration in NHS performance over
OL,16,Fthe past 10 years."
